Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.74,0:00:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.25,0:00:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.65,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.46,0:00:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.18,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.42,0:01:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.76,0:01:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.00,0:01:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.27,0:01:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第73话  紫织母子与犬夜叉的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁  万岁\N太大意了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师输的真惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这真的很深奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种南蛮纸牌游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  这不是纸牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是扑克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗克…牌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是扑克牌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩就安静一点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉也来玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.61,0:03:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在生什么气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情很差呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算呕气铁碎牙也不会变强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗唆  我哪有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.36,0:03:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无法打破它\N连奈落都碰不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.27,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤没效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了  我会越来越强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很让人头大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们不担心\N那种小事我也会想办法解决的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法  要怎么做咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  根本就没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不该期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落结界的问题就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地赶来\N就是为了转告这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.66,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你告诉我\N戈薇的血就让你吸个痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是开玩笑的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.73,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻前往百鬼蝙蝠的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百鬼蝙蝠?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西方海边的某个村子附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个百鬼蝙蝠一族的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个巢穴\N一直受到强力结界保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都奈何不了他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代代都有妖怪在守护结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要斩杀负责守护的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让铁碎牙吸到拥有\N布下强力结界的妖怪之血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩杀强悍的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙就能吸取对手的妖力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是铁碎牙能变强吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…戈薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭妖怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样能让铁碎牙变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百只一千只我都照砍不误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋  你竟敢骗我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说交出你的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子就不会再被袭击了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有好几个人被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说的完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为何还要袭击我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙一定也是\N百鬼蝙蝠的同伙没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不管三七二十一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说百鬼蝙蝠对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我那些家伙巢穴在哪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群人围着\N欺负一个妇女太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巢穴的位置…我们哪知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去问那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说\N那女人明明是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然厚颜无耻的\N生下百鬼蝙蝠的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道百鬼蝙蝠的巢穴后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么…全都宰掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的女儿交给了\N百鬼蝙蝠的这些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百鬼蝙蝠是从以前\N就栖息在这附近的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人与动物当作食物吸血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可怕的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是月夜丸殿下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.84,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的女儿  紫织的父亲\N月夜丸殿下不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.22,0:08:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不仅从未杀过人\N而且自从紫织诞生之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就为我们说服同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这座村子\N没有受到百鬼蝙蝠袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  村子曾经很平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后月夜丸殿下过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也没有阻止他们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百鬼蝙蝠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久  月夜丸殿下的父亲\N紫织的祖父就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:09:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说只要将紫织交给他\N就不再对村子出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大狱丸与月夜丸殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代代肩负着\N守护百鬼蝙蝠巢穴的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承继月夜丸殿下之血的紫织\N是很重要的继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非要那女孩不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那个\N叫大狱丸的家伙担任…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的力量衰退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.46,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦将职务传给别人\N就会丧失力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是除了紫织  没有人\N能胜任守护结界的角色吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖  半~妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫织…你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸上的伤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.85,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  只是摔交而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不小心摔了一交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.87,0:10:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼许久的结果\N我将紫织交给大狱丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先说好!女儿交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换条件是不准再袭击村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.79,0:11:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我答应你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了紫织  你快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不要  爷爷好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  紫织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了村子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要原谅妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.07,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里…你会比较幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧问一句  紫织是半妖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖小鬼有那么大的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的出来你也是半妖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你应该很清楚才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.03,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此既不比妖怪差\N也不比人类差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.74,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫织确实拥有完成使命的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为在那里生活\N是为了那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也能拯救村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.42,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到百鬼蝙蝠他们\N竟然破坏了约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.26,0:12:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你带我去那个\N叫什么来着的老头子那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我一个人就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要找他的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算问我该怎么办我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷  你跟来做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.15,0:13:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  又没什么大不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了谁都不要跟过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快点回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  别这么说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧  犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.54,0:14:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让你饿死就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个洞穴…发光的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让铁碎牙变强的方法是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.87,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是斩杀那女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫织…紫织!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正觉得怎么这么吵\N原来是客人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大狱丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然欺骗我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将紫织交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会袭击村子\N这是你的承诺吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.32,0:15:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信那些话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.46,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以为妖怪的我\N会遵守与人类的约定吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么将紫织还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.67,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.94,0:15:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫织必须一辈子\N在这里做保护结界的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.77,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这丫头继承了亡父月夜丸的能力\N非常的好用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.45,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不觉得她是个\N拥有人类母亲的半妖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母  看样子只能强行讨回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行讨回…办得到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠老头\N不正嚣张的站在紫织前面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能不伤到紫织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只宰掉那个老头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.11,0:16:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之…伤!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将风之伤弹开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.19,0:16:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的百鬼蝙蝠结界\N正如传闻般强韧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子…你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁跟你无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把紫织还来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  人类的奸细吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次可不会失手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  别再打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再伤害妈妈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拼命做好我的工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.07,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要伤害妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.41,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子还比你们懂事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.65,0:17:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少给我乱说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回到村子\N紫织能够过得幸福吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.26,0:17:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村人们都蔑视\N身为半妖之子的紫织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.70,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都一心一意想要自保\N将紫织送到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.77,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能让可爱的孙女\N回到那种令人厌恶的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.80,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大狱丸的话也不是唬人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子不接纳我与紫织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在那里比较…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.24,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪绝对不会\N认同半妖是同伴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是亲人也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很优秀的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是平等的和犬夜叉相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我在保护的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之除非犬夜叉\N将那个结界打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则根本没完没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初也是为了\N这个目的而来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.74,0:19:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩杀布下结界的妖怪\N让刀吸取它的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.51,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能提高铁碎牙的妖力\N打破奈落的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉应该下不了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那个半妖小女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.73,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…我好想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果父亲还活着的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么死了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.01,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还思念着母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.95,0:19:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样子  或许哪天\N会说她想回村子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.32,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只好让他们消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.32,0:20:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个你企盼\N回去的村子还有你母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.44,0:20:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲…半妖是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.62,0:20:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想紫织的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉很温柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.63,0:21:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  我才没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很痛苦吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种我无法想象的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.58,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师和珊瑚\N七宝还有冥加爷爷也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.65,0:21:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我当狗啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.18,0:22:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大群百鬼蝙蝠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.53,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要流多少泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.24,0:22:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart  才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.01,0:22:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.82,0:22:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every Heart  是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.05,0:22:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.73,0:22:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.07,0:23:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.84,0:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.52,0:23:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.26,0:23:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.03,0:23:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.87,0:23:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.62,0:23:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直拼命的保护结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.06,0:23:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要袭击妈妈\N与村子里的大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.06,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小小身体拼命努力的紫织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.06,0:24:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果无法斩杀如此勇敢的她\N铁碎牙就无法增强威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉怎么能下的了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.90,0:24:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!有个唯一的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.57,0:24:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.14,0:24:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破解结界的红色铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.71,0:24:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的思念改变了铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.48,0:24:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.09,0:24:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大狱丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.09,0:24:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼蝙蝠之长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.32,0:24:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将孙女紫织从母亲身边夺走后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让紫织担任保护结界的工作


